Introducing the elite and distinguished panel of speakers for ‘The Luxury Symposium 2022’. Minister of Culture & External Affairs, Meenakshi Lekhi, will grace the event as the chief guest. The event will also see speakers like Queen Diambi Kabatusuila Tshiyoyo Muata, Paulo Gomes, Nafisa Ali, Shazia Ilmi, Rinaa Shah, Subodh Kerkar, Prabha Chandran and Biju Anthony speak about how India has made a mark in the global art and beauty arena.

#baccarose #parcosbeauty #tls2022 #speakers

Parcos is happy to be associated with The Luxury Symposium 2022 as their principal sponsor. The event, organised by The Luxury League, will showcase interactive discussions with world-class creative thinkers, international business leaders, entrepreneurs and senior officials from the government. 
The symposium will not just celebrate and recognise design and innovation, but will also create a platform for creating collaborations between global cultures.

#baccarose #parcosbeauty #tls2022

At Baccarose, we turned this Valentine's Day into a Day of Appreciation, to celebrate not only the hard work, but the GOOD work & Ardent Contribution of our Wonderful Team.
An Appreciation Board was created where colorful notes with kind words of gratitude were written for one another by our ever-enthusiastic team. The exchange of Warm Smiles combined with the reassuring words for one another left the Team with a Truly Content & Happy Heart.

#baccarose #valentinesday #camaraderie #celebration

#Knowyourbrands - "Give a woman the best product you can make, present it in a perfect bottle of beautiful simplicity and impeccable taste, ask for a reasonable price, and you will see the birth of a business the size of which the world has never seen." - François Coty.

Coty, founded in 1904 by François Coty, is a world leader in beauty and has an illustrious roster of cosmetic, skincare and fragrance brands. As a consumer-focused company, Coty’s mission has been to challenge the definition of beauty, encourage authenticity and to celebrate diversity by inclusion. Unique brands powered by global creative elite, that are prestigious and relevant to today’s world.

#Baccarose #Coty #luxury
